name: NFT AMULET CRYPTO MONSTER "BABY MAGGOT" 1st edition
description: My little monsters saved my life and no matter how funny it may sound, they magically inspired me with hope that everything bad will finally pass and golden times will begin full of incredible adventures, discoveries, emotions, acquaintances and opportunities. I love my little monsters, all without exception, but now there are too many of them for me, and therefore I decided to share this miracle monsters with you.
